Package icontrol

This package contains the main Framework of the Instrument Control (iC) program (iC-Framework)

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GUI_Interface
    This interface declares the methods the view needs to implement for the Dispatcher and the Device class.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Dispatcher
    Dispatcher class of Instrument Control.
    GUI_InterfaceMockup
    Mockup View used for JUnit tests.
    iC_ChartXY
    This is a wrapper class for creating JFreeCharts in a convenient way.
    iC_Properties
    Some useful application-wide properties.
    IcontrolAboutBox  
    IcontrolApp
    The main class of the application.
    IcontrolAppMockup
    Mockup for the test environment.
    IcontrolView
    The View-Class that shows and handles the GUI (the application's main frame).
    ScriptMethod
    This class defines a data structure for a Script-Method (a method that is called for a Script-Command with the same name).
    Utilities
    This is collects a set of utility methods used throughout the program.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    AutoGUIAnnotation  
    iC_Annotation
    declare to keep Annotations until Runtime
